{"word":"H3787 - כָּשֵׁר - kâshêr - kaw-share' - Direct - நேரடியாக","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>כָּשֵׁר"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kâshêr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kaw-share'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Direct / நேரடியாக"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பயன்படு, சரி, செவ்வைபாய்ச் செய்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to succeed, to please, to be suitable, to be proper, to be advantageous, to be right and proper to"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to please, to be proper"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil) to give success"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root properly to be <i>straight</i> or <i>right</i>; by implication to <i>be acceptable</i>; also to <i>succeed</i> or proser: - direct, be right, prosper."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3574 - כֹּושָׁרָה - kôwshârâh - ko-shaw-raw'/3574\">H3574</a>, <a href=\"#/H3601 - כִּישֹׁור - kîyshôwr - kee-shore'/3601\">H3601</a>, <a href=\"#/H3787 - כָּשֵׁר - kâshêr - kaw-share'/3787\">H3787</a>, <a href=\"#/H3788 - כִּשְׁרֹון - kishrôwn - kish-rone'/3788\">H3788</a>"}]}